OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Feasing this evening, but a few
OL,7,Fcontinuing overnight, mainly across
OL,8,Fthe north and west. Clear spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping for a time, but further
OL,10,Frain reaching western parts by dawn,
OL,11,Fwhere it will also turn breezy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FA band of rain will move
OL,14,Feastwards throughout Wednesday,
OL,15,Fbecoming slow-moving across parts of
OL,16,FScotland. A mix of sunshine and
OL,17,Fshowers following, with heaviest
OL,18,Fshowers in the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
